00:02:11.930 --> 00:02:14.345
To get started, we're going to take a look at

00:02:14.345 --> 00:02:18.605
a simple comparison just to compare two variables.

00:02:18.605 --> 00:02:27.820
Variable a equal to 10 and also variable b equal to 20.

00:02:27.820 --> 00:02:31.925
We're going to start with a simple if statement just to

00:02:31.925 --> 00:02:35.930
check if the value of a and b is the same.

00:02:35.930 --> 00:02:38.875
To get started, we use the if keyword,

00:02:38.875 --> 00:02:41.299
and then a set of brackets,

00:02:41.299 --> 00:02:45.415
and then after that, a pair of curly braces.

00:02:45.415 --> 00:02:49.205
With an if statement between the brackets here,

00:02:49.205 --> 00:02:51.965
we put a condition to test.

00:02:51.965 --> 00:02:56.075
In our case we want to test if a is equal to b,

00:02:56.075 --> 00:02:58.615
so let's just put that in there, so a,

00:02:58.615 --> 00:03:03.285
and then three equals and then b.

00:03:03.285 --> 00:03:06.050
If you remember, the three equals check if

00:03:06.050 --> 00:03:11.150
the values are equal value and also equal type.

00:03:11.150 --> 00:03:15.425
Let's check if a is equal to b, and then if it is,

00:03:15.425 --> 00:03:20.560
we want to do a document write

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:24.050
and then it prints them out to the browser just to let us

00:03:24.050 --> 00:03:27.050
know that the condition is true.

00:03:27.050 --> 00:03:32.765
I'm just going to write condition is true and just make it a little bit bigger.

00:03:32.765 --> 00:03:36.480
Let's put some level 2 heading tags in there.

00:03:37.160 --> 00:03:40.800
So h2 before and after,

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:46.150
and then let's open the app in the browser and see what happens.

00:03:47.420 --> 00:03:51.935
Again, nothing is showing in the browser because the condition is not true,

00:03:51.935 --> 00:03:53.840
because a is not equal to b.

00:03:53.840 --> 00:04:00.200
If we just change both the values to be the same and then refresh,

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:02.600
we should now get the message condition is true.

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:07.085
The if statement is all working correctly.

00:04:07.085 --> 00:04:08.720
As well as the three equals,

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:12.065
there's many different other comparisons we can use.

00:04:12.065 --> 00:04:15.530
We mentioned earlier on that using two equal symbols will

00:04:15.530 --> 00:04:19.040
check if a and b is equal value but not equal type.

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:22.505
For example, one could be a string and one could be a number.

00:04:22.505 --> 00:04:25.520
If we want to check if the values are not equal,

00:04:25.520 --> 00:04:29.465
we use a exclamation mark and then an equal symbol.

00:04:29.465 --> 00:04:33.140
Let's just change that to be not equal and we should still get

00:04:33.140 --> 00:04:37.210
the condition is true, which we do there.

00:04:37.210 --> 00:04:39.480
This checks for the value.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:42.485
If you wanted to check for the value and type,

00:04:42.485 --> 00:04:46.345
we could use two equals and the exclamation mark.

00:04:46.345 --> 00:04:50.145
This means not equal value or type.

00:04:50.145 --> 00:04:54.365
We can also use less than or greater than.

00:04:54.365 --> 00:04:56.360
If a is greater than b,

00:04:56.360 --> 00:05:01.010
which it is, the condition is still true.

00:05:01.010 --> 00:05:04.460
If a was less than b,

00:05:04.460 --> 00:05:09.100
it should now be blank because the condition is false.

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:12.395
Combining the less than and greater than with

00:05:12.395 --> 00:05:17.540
a equals symbol means if a is less than or equal to b,

00:05:17.540 --> 00:05:20.180
then run this code between the braces,

00:05:20.180 --> 00:05:23.185
and exactly the same with the greater than.

00:05:23.185 --> 00:05:26.660
If a is greater than or equal to b,

00:05:26.660 --> 00:05:30.860
the condition is true. Let's refresh that.

00:05:30.860 --> 00:05:34.175
This is true because a is greater than b.

00:05:34.175 --> 00:05:36.905
If b was also 20,

00:05:36.905 --> 00:05:38.585
so they were equal,

00:05:38.585 --> 00:05:41.835
we should also still get condition is true.

00:05:41.835 --> 00:05:44.370
Good. So I hope that makes sense.

