00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:51.055
use of how this can be used in a real life program.

00:05:51.055 --> 00:05:57.895
I'm going to just check if a user is logged in and also check the user's name.

00:05:57.895 --> 00:06:01.670
An if statement could check if a user is logged in and

00:06:01.670 --> 00:06:06.305
then print to the browser a welcome message to that logged in user.

00:06:06.305 --> 00:06:11.210
With a variable such as logged in,

00:06:11.210 --> 00:06:16.500
I want to set this to a boolean value of true.

00:06:17.570 --> 00:06:21.015
This can be either true or false.

00:06:21.015 --> 00:06:25.910
Then a variable which stores the user's name.

00:06:25.910 --> 00:06:29.160
I want to set mine to Chris.

00:06:29.210 --> 00:06:31.250
Then just as before,

00:06:31.250 --> 00:06:33.900
we'll create a if statement.

00:06:36.620 --> 00:06:40.310
If you just want to check if a user is logged in,

00:06:40.310 --> 00:06:43.670
we can just check if logged in.

00:06:43.670 --> 00:06:47.900
We don't need to use any comparison operators such as equals,

00:06:47.900 --> 00:06:52.800
because this is already set to true. Open the variable.

00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:55.305
If the user is logged in,

00:06:55.305 --> 00:07:00.880
let's create a message for that user with a document write.

00:07:02.150 --> 00:07:04.530
This can be as simple,

00:07:04.530 --> 00:07:06.770
or as complicated as you want.

00:07:06.770 --> 00:07:12.230
I'm just going to create a welcome message to that user and then add

00:07:12.230 --> 00:07:17.735
onto the end of that welcome message the variable name of the user.

00:07:17.735 --> 00:07:20.120
This should say, welcome Chris.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:26.490
Then lets open the browser. There we go.

00:07:26.490 --> 00:07:30.635
We get the welcome message because the user is set to logged in.

00:07:30.635 --> 00:07:38.435
If you change this to be false and then refresh the browser again,

00:07:38.435 --> 00:07:43.685
we should lose the message because this condition is no longer met.

00:07:43.685 --> 00:07:46.860
I hope that all makes sense to you now.

